{"tid":2335641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員稱遭雷射光襲擊 眼球刺痛視力模糊但仍駕駛 供稱未覺危險不用停車","createTime":"2020-12-22T04:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T05:35:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ee0e3350e0b6a7ecbf66406080f072b86443d3","tid":2335641,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"年初中環遮打花園「天下制裁」集會被警方腰斬，混亂收場。當晚大埔有警員駕駛警車時，聲稱感受到50米外行人天橋上有雷射光射向他，遂駛至天橋底並與隊員下車追捕疑人，最終拘捕一名褲袋內疑藏有雷射筆的學生。學生被控襲警等兩罪受審，警員供稱當時沒有「想快啲捉到個犯」的念頭，他只是開着警車閃燈和警號，駛過天橋底往前方迴旋處掉頭，到第二次駛經橋底時才下車捉人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201222/CIRG2ACZVVFAVMYTXYXV4DJLXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201222%2FCIRG2ACZVVFAVMYTXYXV4DJLXE%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=4f26f37e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201222%2FCIRG2ACZVVFAVMYTXYXV4DJLXE%2F&h=5dc65c0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201222/CIRG2ACZVVFAVMYTXYXV4DJLXE/</a>"},{"pid":"b39edf6816cf22428d01f8f6483e9ff3eefcdc68","tid":2335641,"uid":4942,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"講大話講到自己都兜唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14593d43806fb94a40d08d2ae60bfa677350cf2a","tid":2335641,"uid":82938,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"視力濛但渣車<br />\n即係攞香港人條命玩"},{"pid":"572adbe5dcb826da7b5b1ed998523c39599c2639","tid":2335641,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:53:54.000Z","msg